{
  "stem": "802.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Now, because my mother insisted that both my sister and I take a spoon of her soup whenever the soup was doled out, which was once a day, and a ration of bread in the morning.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You know, it was a starvation diet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But my mother was a mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So we used to quarrel with her because we didn't want to take her soup.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And so we-- we created a little bit of noise, as a result of which we were sent to a punitive barrack in Majdanek that was run by a Polish woman, and there was a kapo who was very, very sadistic.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "She kind of took a liking to me because I was maybe a little bit more gentle than some people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I didn't push so much for the soup.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Because you lined up for the soup.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And you had to be in the right place because if you were the first one on line, you got very thin soup.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "If you were the last one, and the soup was thicker on the bottom of the barrel, you know, then you wouldn't get anything.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So you had to find a strategy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But one-- so we all tried.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, if you didn't try, you couldn't live.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you gave up, you couldn't live.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you didn't believe that you're going to survive, there was just no way that you could survive, which is not to say that we did anything extraordinary because everything was largely by chance.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People were killed largely by chance because they were in that particular place-- everybody was to be killed.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
